== 借往其他语言的单词 ==
俄语里（{{lang|ru|тундра}}）及英语里（{{lang|en|tundra}}）的单词“[[冻原|冻原]]”是来自基尔丁萨米语。在基尔丁萨米语里，单词“{{lang|sjd|тӯндар}}”的意思为“没有树木的平原”，其[[属格|所有格]]的形式为“{{lang|sjd|тӯндра}}”。<ref name="Aapala">{{cite web | url = https://www.kotus.fi/nyt/kolumnit_artikkelit_ja_esitelmat/kieli-ikkuna_%281996_2010%29/tunturista_jangalle | title = Tunturista jängälle | author = Aapala, Kirsti | language = fi | publisher = Kotus | date = 1999-08-24 | accessdate = 2020-07-18 | archive-date = 2020-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200612175233/https://www.kotus.fi/nyt/kolumnit_artikkelit_ja_esitelmat/kieli-ikkuna_%281996_2010%29/tunturista_jangalle | dead-url = no }}</ref>

